{"tid":1397454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武唔好買淘寶，但係和理非呢？？？？","createTime":"2019-08-02T13:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:02:45.000Z","uid":73392,"like":39,"dislike":257,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"67d35f27d4e0607abd98860e559ded1fa460b6e4","tid":1397454,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好屌曬鬼住，耐心睇曬先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先，唔係淘寶買gear嘅最大原因，只係怕會暴露訊息，鎖定班勇武，如果可以解決呢個問題，淘寶根本係好好嘅抗爭工具</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武唔好買淘寶，原因唔洗多講，但係和理非其實應該狂係淘寶買gear先啱哦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一來和理非買gear，可以掩護係淘寶買gear嘅勇武，試諗下想衝嘅係淘寶買，百幾個訂單，好易查，但係如果和理非同勇武一齊買，成萬張單，有一半都和理非買黎放係屋企，咁就算係屋企搵到有gear都唔可以證明d咩<br />\n<br />\n二來淘寶真係平，好多手足唔食飯，攞錢買gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起就心痛<br />\n<br />\n最好嘅做法係，和理非（唔留夜果班）買gear現場送比勇武，咁樣就可以以低成本獲得gear之餘，比狗查嘅和理非，根本夜晚就唔係現場，咩都入唔到，一舉兩得唔好咩？"},{"pid":"2ff76410cbe425d2c667ca1bc1abb48c4b90cd54","tid":1397454,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2cb2746dd977450918bf1c94a9c74826cc3f8f9","tid":1397454,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81507ee74e10670021d25c721d393992a8d9628b","tid":1397454,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d705067e3c4cb5070397eb40bc426fa861021548","tid":1397454,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":